eDeck Version 3.4.4 </strong></p>\n<p>On selecting the spine position &#8216;Horizontal&#8217; in Navigation Options, the spines are displayed horizontally and the selected slide moves upwards on navigation.</p>\n<p><img class="size-large wp-image-17426 aligncenter" src="http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/rosespine-580x345.jpeg" alt="Horizontal Spine in Classic Lens" width="580" height="345" /></p>\n<p>Options -&gt; Navigation -&gt; Spine Position -&gt; Horizontal</p>\n<p><img class="size-large wp-image-17427 aligncenter" src="http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/horizontalspine-580x414.jpeg" alt="Options for horizontal spine" width="580" height="414" /></p>\n<p><a href="http://demo.slidedeck.com/slidedeck-classic-lens/"><img class="size-full wp-image-17277 aligncenter" src="http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Try-the-free-demoButton.png" alt="Try the free demo" width="182" height="46" /></a></p>\n<p><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/"><img class="size-full wp-image-16026 aligncenter" src="http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/get_slidedeck.png" alt="Get SlideDeck3" width="272" height="60" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<br/><br/><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/?utm_source=feed_ad&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=sd_blog"><img src="//s3.amazonaws.com/assets-slidedeck2/wp-content/themes/slidedeck2/images/sd-rss.jpg" alt="Easily create AWESOME WordPress sliders - Get SlideDeck" style="display:block;border:none;"/></a><div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=95kEA4dZphA:JseNCwQpNZ4:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=95kEA4dZphA:JseNCwQpNZ4:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=95kEA4dZphA:JseNCwQpNZ4:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=95kEA4dZphA:JseNCwQpNZ4:V_s