r. New addons, unique lenses and quick bug fixes were a regular thing. Here&#8217;s 2015 in a nutshell &#8211;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/slidedeck-3-0-released/" target="_blank">SlideDeck 3.0 Released</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/slidedeck-3-1-released/" target="_blank">SlideDeck 3.1 Released</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/scheduler-addon-released/" target="_blank">SlideDeck Scheduler Addon Released</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/prime-lens-up-for-grabs/" target="_blank">Prime Lens Up For Grabs</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/update-prime-lens-now-supports-all-14-dynamic-sources/" target="_blank">Update – Prime Lens Now Supports All 14 Dynamic Sources</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/importexport-slider-addon-released/" target="_blank">Import / Export Slider Addon Released</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/create-sliders-on-any-website-using-the-slidedeck-app/" target="_blank">Create sliders on any website using the SlideDeck App</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/update-pinterest-pin-it-button-now-on-your-slidedecks/" target="_blank">Update – Pinterest Pin It Button Now on Your Slidedecks</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/slidedeck-3-2-4-released/" target="_blank">SlideDeck 3.2.4 Released</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/parfocal-lens-get-your-slider-images-moving-2/" target="_blank">Parfocal Lens – Get your slider images moving</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/slidedeck-3-2-6-released/" target="_blank">SlideDeck 3.2.6 Released</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/there-is-intelligent-life-in-this-slider/" target="_blank">Launching new Lead Generation Addon</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/slidedeck-3-now-integrates-with-woocommerce-products/" target="_blank">SlideDeck 3 now integrates with WooCommerce Products</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/news-updates/slidedeck3-3-3-2-released/" target="_blank">SlideDeck 3.3.2 Released</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/slidedeck-version-3-3-3-will-try-to-fix-you/" target="_blank">SlideDeck Version 3.3.3 will try to fix you</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/slidedeck-version-3-3-4-released/" target="_blank">SlideDeck Version 3.3.4 Released</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/slidedeck-version-3-3-5-released/" target="_blank">SlideDeck Version 3.3.5 Released</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/roses-in-december-share-warmth-with-sliders-that-go-viral/" target="_blank">Roses in December – Share warmth with sliders that go viral</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/a-brand-new-lens-with-parallax-effect/" target="_blank">A brand new lens with Parallax effect</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/slidedeck-version-3-4-1-released/" target="_blank">SlideDeck Version 3.4.1 Released</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/slidedeck-version-3-4-2-released/" target="_blank">SlideDeck Version 3.4.2 Released</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/slidedeck-version-3-4-3-released/" target="_blank">SlideDeck Version 3.4.3 Released</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>This is how we guzzled down a lot of coffee in 2015 ! And, we are back to the grind . Lot more coming up.</p>\n<p>Cheers,</p>\n<p>Team SlideDeck</p>\n<br/><br/><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/?utm_source=feed_ad&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=sd_blog"><img src="//s3.amazonaws.com/assets-slidedeck2/wp-content/themes/slidedeck2/images/sd-rss.jpg" alt="Easily create AWESOME WordPress sliders - Get SlideDeck" style="display:block;border:none;"/></a><div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=