ve resolved the following issues &#8211;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Issue in Prime Lens Image Scaling Option &#8216;Scale proportionally and do not crop&#8217; for images having height less than the container resolved</li>\n<li>Loop issue in slide transition effect for all lenses resolved</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Grab SlideDeck3 and create the perfect sliders for your website</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-16026" src="http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/get_slidedeck.png" alt="Get SlideDeck3" width="272" height="60" /></a></p>\n<br/><br/><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/?utm_source=feed_ad&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=sd_blog"><img src="//s3.amazonaws.com/assets-slidedeck2/wp-content/themes/slidedeck2/images/sd-rss.jpg" alt="Easily create AWESOME WordPress sliders - Get SlideDeck" style="display:block;border:none;"/></a><div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=BA2WcFdUqc4:KO8uDqY0irQ:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=BA2WcFdUqc4:KO8uDqY0irQ:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=BA2WcFdUqc4:KO8uDqY0irQ:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=BA2WcFdUqc4:KO8uDqY0irQ:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=BA2WcFdUqc4:KO8uDqY0irQ:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=BA2WcFdUqc4:KO8uDqY0irQ:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=BA2WcFdUqc4:KO8uDqY0irQ:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=BA2WcFdUqc4:KO8uDqY0irQ:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/Sl