:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:33:"http://www.slidedeck.com/?p=17327";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:305:"With 2016 around the corner, SlideDeck has yet another new release. SlideDeck Version 3.4.1 has these bugs fixed for you, right on time! Have a look &#8211; Issue with Classic Lens for dynamic content sources resolved. Now, slides having no images, for example content sourced from Your Posts, are also...";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"Neha";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2892:"<p>With 2016 around the corner, SlideDeck has yet another new release.<br />\n<strong>SlideDeck Version 3.4.1</strong> has these bugs fixed for you, right on time! Have a look &#8211;</p>\n<p><img class="size-large wp-image-17328 aligncenter" src="http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/newss-580x340.jpeg" alt="newss" width="580" height="340" /></p>\n<p>Issue with <strong>Classic Lens</strong> for <strong>dynamic</strong> content sources resolved. Now, slides having no images, for example content sourced from <strong>Your Posts</strong>, are also displayed properly.</p>\n<p><img class="size-large wp-image-17329 aligncenter" src="http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/screenshotfor2-1-580x505.png" alt="screenshotfor2 (1)" width="580" height="505" /></p>\n<p>&#8216;Scale proportionally and crop&#8217; option in &#8216;<strong>Image Scaling</strong>&#8216; now applies the <strong>full width</strong> of the image to the slide (<strong> no blank spaces around the image </strong>)</p>\n<p><a href="http://demo.slidedeck.com/wp-login.php"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-17277 size-full" src="http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Try-the-free-demoButton.png" alt="Try the free demo" width="182" height="46" /></a></p>\n<p><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-16026 size-full" src="http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/get_slidedeck.png" alt="Get SlideDeck3" width="272" height="60" /></a></p>\n<br/><br/><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/?utm_source=feed_ad&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=sd_blog"><img src="//s3.amazonaws.com/assets-slidedeck2/wp-content/themes/slidedeck2/images/sd-rss.jpg" alt="Easily create AWESOME WordPress sliders - Get SlideDeck" style="display:block;border:none;"/></a><div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=i0S2vHT9wxk:IeQh9et7ebs:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=i0S2vHT9wxk:IeQh9et7ebs:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=i0S2vHT9wxk:IeQh9et7ebs:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=i0S2vHT9wxk:IeQh9et7ebs:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=i0S2vHT9wxk:IeQh9et7ebs:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=i0S2vHT9wxk:IeQh9et7ebs:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=i0S2vHT9wxk:IeQh9et7ebs:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=i0S2vHT9wxk:IeQh9et7ebs:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/Slidedeck/~4/i0S2vHT9wxk" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"c