s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:33:"http://www.slidedeck.com/?p=17273";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:306:"&#160; &#8220;Parallax effect&#8221; is a buzzword in web design. And SlideDeck version 3.4.0 brings you a lens which helps in making Parallax image sliders. Hook your visitors with sliders that scroll as they scroll down or images which move with each cursor movement. Layer your base image with upto 3...";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"Neha";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3427:"<p><img class="size-large wp-image-17274 aligncenter" src="http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/ezgif.com-optimize-580x389.gif" alt="Parallax Lens" width="580" height="389" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&#8220;<strong>Parallax effec</strong>t&#8221; is a buzzword in web design. And <strong>SlideDeck version 3.4.0</strong> brings you a lens which helps in making <strong>Parallax</strong> image sliders. Hook your visitors with sliders that scroll as they scroll down or images which move with each cursor movement.</p>\n<p>Layer your base image with upto 3 more images and a caption image!</p>\n<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Parallax Lens</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Mouse movement Parallax</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img class="size-large wp-image-17275 aligncenter" src="http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/mouse-movement-parallax-580x280.png" alt="Mouse Movement Parallax" width="580" height="280" /></p>\n<p>As seen in the image, you can add upto 3 layered images to a base image, and a caption image</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Scroll Parallax</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img class="size-full wp-image-17276 aligncenter" src="http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/scroll-parallax.png" alt="scroll parallax" width="575" height="275" /></p>\n<p>Base image and a caption image ; a slider which scrolls as the visitor scrolls down, the Parallax effect</p>\n<p><a href="http://demo.slidedeck.com/custom-slidedeck-parallax-lens/"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-17277 size-full" src="http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Try-the-free-demoButton.png" alt="Try the free demo" width="182" height="46" /></a></p>\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Grab SlideDeck3 and layer your images in style with the new Parallax lens</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/"><img class="alignnone wp-image-16026 size-full" src="http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/get_slidedeck.png" alt="Get SlideDeck3" width="272" height="60" /></a></p>\n<br/><br/><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/?utm_source=feed_ad&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=sd_blog"><img src="//s3.amazonaws.com/assets-slidedeck2/wp-content/themes/slidedeck2/images/sd-rss.jpg" alt="Easily create AWESOME WordPress sliders - Get SlideDeck" style="display:block;border:none;"/></a><div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=cnzJX8CsqaU:D2NO6DmNeec:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=cnzJX8CsqaU:D2NO6DmNeec:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=cnzJX8CsqaU:D2NO6DmNeec:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=cnzJX8CsqaU:D2NO6DmNeec:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=cnzJX8CsqaU:D2NO6DmNeec:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a