:{s:4:"data";s:4:"Neha";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2919:"<p>We&#8217;ve been concentrating on bug fixes, as evident from the last 2 releases. Here&#8217;s a quick look at what&#8217;s in place now. The best slider plugin is really getting even better <img src="http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/simple-smile.png" alt=":)" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p>\n<h2><strong>Bug Fixes :</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>In the <strong>custom video source</strong>, under the image scaling option, &#8216;scale proportionally and do not crop&#8217; shows a video with correct aspect ratio now</li>\n<li><strong>SlideDeck widget</strong> at the front end has been fixed (when &#8216;Always load SlideDeck JSS/CSS on every page is OFF)</li>\n<li>In <strong>Reporter lens</strong>, title length issue has been resolved ( even if the title length is less than 100 characters, it is displayed without any ellipses now )</li>\n<li>The issue related to <strong>positioning of slides</strong> has been fixed ( Even if the last slide is set as the start slide, the last slide is displayed properly)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>Opt for the slider plugin that has continous and exciting updates !</strong></em></p>\n<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Get SlideDeck3 NOW !</strong></h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/" target="_blank"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-16026" src="http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/get_slidedeck.png" alt="Get SlideDeck3" width="272" height="60" /></a></p>\n<br/><br/><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/?utm_source=feed_ad&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=sd_blog"><img src="//s3.amazonaws.com/assets-slidedeck2/wp-content/themes/slidedeck2/images/sd-rss.jpg" alt="Easily create AWESOME WordPress sliders - Get SlideDeck" style="display:block;border:none;"/></a><div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=7b4Gj0L62Vg:dmeN-VOfRDE:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=7b4Gj0L62Vg:dmeN-VOfRDE:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=7b4Gj0L62Vg:dmeN-VOfRDE:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=7b4Gj0L62Vg:dmeN-VOfRDE:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=7b4Gj0L62Vg:dmeN-VOfRDE:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=7b4Gj0L62Vg:dmeN-VOfRDE:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=7b4Gj0L62Vg:dmeN-VOfRDE:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=7b4Gj0L62Vg:dmeN-VOfRDE:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/Slidedeck/~4/7b4Gj0L62Vg" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:68:"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/slidedeck-version-3-3-5-released/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:63:"http://www.slidedeck.com/blog/slidedeck-version-3-3-5-released/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:48:"\